	<ul>
		<li>Contact the Mammography Accreditation Program at (512) 834-6688 ext. 2246, at least 30 days prior to facility opening date, for information regarding the required documents, the correct forms and fees.</li>
	</ul>
	
	<p>If the <strong><em>American College of Radiology (ACR)</em></strong> will be the mammography accreditation body:</p>
